         <head>
            <hi rend="bold">ERRATA. </hi>
         </head>
         <list type="errata">
            <item>Preface, p. xi. line 11, for Lucretia—read
                                   Lucretius.</item>
            <item>Page 145, line 1, vol. ii. place a comma after the words <lb/>
                                   “disconsolate creature,” and omit the comma after
                                   “perhaps”</item>
            <item>Page 147, line 5, vol. ii. for “both grey red and
                                   green,” <lb/> substitute grey, scarlet, and green.</item>
         </list>
